targets.query: SELECT sum("ddb_set_task_finished_succeeded")  / 10 FROM /^$pod_id$/ WHERE $timeFilter GROUP BY time(10s) fill(none)
SELECT sum("ddb_set_task_finished_succeeded") * -1 FROM "agent_post" WHERE $timeFilter AND ("str_pod_id" = '$pod_id' OR '$pod_id' = 'All') GROUP BY time(10s) fill(null)

panels.description: Count of Agent's that have finished at least one task within last minute. When queue is full, this number should be equal to the total number of pods in the system
panels.title: Active Agent's Count

targets.query: SELECT mean("task_exec_time_ms") FROM "agent_post" WHERE $timeFilter AND "task_id" =~ /^$task_id$/ GROUP BY time($__interval) fill(null)
